Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:57.80,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(950,950)\pos(495,478)\fsp5\blur2}火焰的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.25,0:01:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这架势 想动手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.47,0:01:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别以为骗得了我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样 轰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.43,0:02:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的任务可是押送丸铁去京城啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人我无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家人以及弟弟 都被他杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁杀了你的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五年前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我亲眼看到这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失火了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火势好大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有人在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放火烧你家的歹徒已经查明身份了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个人称不忍的强盗团伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都是冷血无情的极恶之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抢完民宅的值钱货之后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还会杀了全家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了除掉所有的目击者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父母的遗体找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但由于火势蔓延过快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄的年龄也小
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕尸骨无存了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 忘了你弟弟的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来讽刺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易找到杀害弟弟和父母的凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却因为任务必须将他押送去京城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经是独当一面的警务人员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.35,0:06:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不再是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想因为个人恩怨而影响任务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到他早晚会被处死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内心总有些冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻眼前的他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在烈焰中杀了弟弟的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是你弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受死吧 丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是满手血腥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:07:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了许多无辜百姓的坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的任务是将他安全地押送到京城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管什么任务 他杀了我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许丸铁确实是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你不能杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正没有人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个森林是绝佳的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有人看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰 你冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可在看着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会 没人会看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你不说出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 干脆把你也杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想什么 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在非常冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了 只能和你一搏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 刚才的气势呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别躲了 快现身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再欺负丸铁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把丸铁放了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们到底是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们跟丸铁是什么关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点 有话好好说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不是忍者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小朋友舞刀弄枪的很危险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小李 该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对小孩子下不了手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要替死去的父母和弟弟报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静下来 再仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀了你弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜 丸铁 你别过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:10:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些线比钢铁还硬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人力是绝对无法扯断的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不忍的文殊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁我就带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要得到他 你们就没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些线会随着气温上升而缩紧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在痛苦中死去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半小时后 你们就会四分五裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 我可不想死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将丸铁安全押送去京城的任务还没完成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜 你先搞清自己的状况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都快性命不保了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不觉得那些不忍会把丸铁当成同伴对待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁没有骗我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些不忍搞不好会杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才想先杀了他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁离开时 不是大喊你的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他应该是有话要告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想听那种人渣捏造的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我始终觉得丸铁不是十恶不赦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在丸铁说出心里话之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们谈谈吧 一定会有解决方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 可以了 不要再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你们是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以刚才误以为你们是不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是木叶的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次任务是负责保护押送丸铁的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们能不能放了丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都是被丸铁从不忍手中救出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他救了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些孩子是孤儿 父母都被不忍杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁不忍心杀小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以偷偷背着不忍救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁一直照顾着我们这些孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是不忍干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们的遭遇和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你并不孤单 我们会陪你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今天起 我们就是你的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要脱离不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忍不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再跟他们一起当强盗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么做 他们不会放过你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定去偷他们的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后故意让警务省逮捕我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那时 他们为了夺回我 一定会露脸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样警务省就能将他们一网打尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用自己当诱饵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随后丸铁真的偷了不忍的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后被捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们担心丸铁会出事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以来到这座森林
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原以为不忍会被抓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那丸铁是真心悔过 所以才背叛了不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:14:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须想办法抓捕那些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正十恶不赦的不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不忍怎样与我们无关
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的是救出丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁应该和鸣人在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心 丸铁不会被不忍带走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去真要完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汗水渗进去后 绳子就松了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:15:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没骗你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就习惯这种蛇的毒性了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我始终觉得丸铁不是十恶不赦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何 我要当丸铁的面问个清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也得找到丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后替父母和我弟弟报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差点就没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 赶快去救丸铁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要找到他 并亲手杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人的确是丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那几个小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不忍的文殊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把丸铁放了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会放过你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪儿来的小鬼 真没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁 他们居然让我把你还给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要还也是还给我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的不忍 我要为家人报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼 给我乖乖听话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文殊 快放了那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么资格命令我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说的报仇是怎么回事啊 丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍法.铁丝网
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的 这个网坚不可破
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回答我的问题 丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那就看看我的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 我会说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再伤害他了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始乖乖听话不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些孩子是不忍袭击的家庭的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我偷偷救了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 你早就背叛我们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:20:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 钱就藏在他们那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些钱本来就是这些孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这叛徒 别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.44,0:20:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位久等了 漩涡鸣人拜见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 你平安无事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你把丸铁带走的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:20:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里就是不忍的老窝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.88,0:22:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 明雄应该就在那栋房子里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.00,0:22:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会放过那些不忍的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破坏亲兄弟重逢 简直岂有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我们上吧 浓眉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.19,0:22:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕敌人曾经是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.46,0:22:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要一举消灭他们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.10,0:23:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺回轰的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.96,0:23:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各奔前程
